            "title": "Do you have any coupon codes?",
            "answer": "<p>We donâ€™t. So if you see anyone on the internet offering a â€œXero Shoes coupon codeâ€ they are scamming you.</p><p>We do have occasional specials and sales that youâ€™ll hear about if you subscribe to ourÂ <a href=\"/pages/newsletter\" title=\"Xero Shoes Newsletter\">newsletter</a>Â or follow us onÂ <a href=\"https://facebook.com/xeroshoes/\">Facebook</a>,Â <a href=\"https://instagram.com/xeroshoes/\">Instagram</a>,Â <a href=\"https://youtube.com/xeroshoes/\">YouTube</a>, orÂ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/xeroshoes/\">Twitter</a>.</p>",
