            "title": "Do you offer military discounts?",
            "answer": "<p>We do offer active military personnel a 15% discount on orders placed through xeroshoes.com!<br/>Here in the US, we use GovX ID, a free third-party service, to verify your affiliation. You can find more information through the following link:Â <a href=\"/pages/military-discount\" title=\"Military/First Responders & Healthcare Discounts\">https://xeroshoes.com/pages/military-discount</a></p><p>For those of you outside of the United States, since GovX ID wouldnâ€™t be used internationally, we would just ask for a proof of service.<br/>EmailÂ <a href=\"mailto:support@xeroshoes.com\">support@xeroshoes.com</a>Â from a government email account or send a copy of your Military ID. Once that has been received, we will email you directions about how get your military discount.</p>",
