        "faq_subitem_ywKhm7": {
          "type": "faq_subitem",
          "settings": {
            "parent_title": "Shipping & Handling",
            "title": "Do you deliver to my country?",
            "answer": "<p>Weâ€™ve sent Xero Shoes to 97 countries around the world.</p><p>Sadly, though, we have had to discontinue shipping packages to certain countries due to unreliable delivery, notably Mexico, Indonesia, and Brazil.</p><p>To find out if we ship to your location, you can either add items to your cart and go through the checkout process â€” if you donâ€™t see your country, then we may not deliver there.</p><p>You can also ask Customer Happiness Team â€” emailÂ <a href=\"mailto:support@xeroshoes.com\">support@xeroshoes.com</a>Â or call 303.447.3100 (thatâ€™s always the fastest way)</p><p>If you live in a country that we canâ€™t ship to, you may want to look into the following courier services that may be able to forward packages to your location:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.shipito.com/\">https://www.shipito.com/</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.bonvu.com/\">https://www.bonvu.com/</a></p><p>Another option â€” see if we have a store near you that can ship to you â€”Â <a href=\"/pages/stores\" title=\"Xero Shoes Stores\">https://xeroshoes.com/pages/stores/</a></p><p>Also we have a few styles available on Amazon.</p><p>Weâ€™ve heard that many international customers ship their shoes to friends or family in the US, UK, or Australia who will be visiting soon.</p>",
            "answer_html": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_subitem_VwybbE": {
          "type": "faq_subitem",
          "settings": {
            "parent_title": "Shipping & Handling",
            "title": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "answer": "<p>We do! Weâ€™ve sold Xero Shoes to people inÂ <strong>more than 97 countries</strong>Â around the world.</p><p>We use the US Postal service or DHL to send our shipments. The cost to ship will depend on the weight of the package and the delivery speed you select; several options will be provided at checkout.</p><p>Limited tracking is available for some Standard and First Class International shipments depending on the country. Full tracking is available with all Priority Express and Express International shipments.</p><p>Though almost all of our international orders arrive without incident, we strongly advise you to select Priority Express International or Express International if you live in a country with a less reliable postal service. We cannot guarantee delivery of packages shipped using First Class International.</p><p>At this time, weâ€™ve stopped shipping to Brazil, Mexico or Indonesia due to poor delivery. See the FAQ â€œDo You Deliver to my Countryâ€ for more details and options if youâ€™re in those countries.</p><p>International delivery can take anywhere from 3 days to 8 weeks depending on how long your order spends in customs at the border.</p><p>Please note that some countries do require the payment of import duties for international shipments above a certain value. We advise you to know the import regulations of your country and understand that you will be responsible for payment of any duties and fees imposed by your government at the border.</p><p>All packages will be marked as merchandise; as a commercial shipper, we are not able to mark a package as a gift (if youâ€™re giving Xero Shoes as a gift, thatâ€™s not the same as us sending a gift).</p><p>Also, check our store locator atÂ <a href=\"/pages/stores\" title=\"Xero Shoes Stores\">www.xeroshoes.com/pages/stores/</a>. There may be a Xero Shoes dealer closer to you.</p>",
            "answer_html": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_subitem_xMh88r": {
          "type": "faq_subitem",
          "settings": {
            "parent_title": "Shipping & Handling",
            "title": "How long does it take to get my order?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Note: Due to the current COVID-19 pandemic, some shipping services may be delayed, and due to heavy order volume during the holidays, it may take longer for your order to be shipped. We thank you for your patience as it may take two weeks or longer for your package to arrive.</strong></p><p>Shipping time depends on what you order, where your package is going, and how fast you want it delivered.</p><p>When you get to the Checkout page, youâ€™ll see different options and prices before youâ€™re asked for payment information.</p><p>Typical shipping domestic shipping times are:</p><ul><li>Our Flat Rate shipping takes 5-10 business days on average.</li><li>First ClassÂ  â€“ estimated 4-9 business days â€“ can be slower during high volume mail times</li><li>Priority Mail â€“ 2 or 3 business days</li><li>Priority Express Mail â€“ 1 or 2 business days</li></ul><p>Please note that USPS does not guarantee delivery times for First Class and Priority Mail.</p><p>For International deliveries, here are some typical times:</p><ul><li>DHL Packet Plus â€“ 2-3 weeks average, may take longer depending on receiving country*</li><li>First Class â€“ 1-3 weeks average, may take up to 8 depending on receiving country*</li><li>Priority Mail â€“ 6-10 business days*</li><li>Priority Mail Express â€“ 3-5 business days*</li></ul><p>* International delivery times may be increased by additional customs processing times at the border.</p><p>Full tracking is available for items shipped with DHL International shipping and USPS Priority Express International shipments.</p><p>You may also want to check for a retailerÂ  near you atÂ <a href=\"/pages/stores\" title=\"Xero Shoes Stores\">www.xeroshoes.com/pages/stores/</a>.</p><p>You can find more information about shipping here:Â <a href=\"/pages/shipping\" title=\"Shipping\">www.xeroshoes.com/pages/shipping</a></p>",
            "answer_html": ""
          }
        },
