            "title": "How do I adjust my sandals to fit?",
            "answer": "<p>Lena likes to say thereâ€™s a â€œsweet spotâ€ for sandal strap tension and position. Some people find it right away and others take a bit of time.</p><p>Go toÂ <a href=\"/blogs/blog/adjust-for-the-perfect-fit\" title=\"How to Adjust the Xero Shoes Sandals for a Perfect Fit\">https://xeroshoes.com/blogs/blog/adjust-for-the-perfect-fit</a>Â for more info and suggestions.</p>",
