          "type": "faq_subitem",
          "settings": {
            "parent_title": "About the shoes you received",
            "title": "My shoe broke. What do I do?",
            "answer": "<p>While we stand behind the quality of our products, we also know reality: nothing is perfect and nothing goes 100% according to plan. Thatâ€™s why we have a 2 Year Manufacturerâ€™s Warranty.</p><p>There are more details about our warrantyÂ <a href=\"/pages/warranty\" title=\"Xero Shoes Warranty\">here</a>.</p><p>Please emailÂ <a href=\"mailto:support@xeroshoes.com\">support@xeroshoes.com</a>Â or call us at 1-800-499-8880 or 303.447.3100 so we can evaluate your situation and give you the correct remedy options.</p>",
