          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the affiliate program work?",
            "answer": "<p>When you sign up, youâ€™ll get a special link (â€œaffiliate linkâ€) to use to promote Xero Shoes. You can share this link on your social media, in emails, any website you have, or even in person.Â </p><p>Youâ€™ll also get access to ready-made banners, images, and other creative assets you can use in your promotions.Â </p><p>Youâ€™ll earn commissions on sales made by people who are first referred to Xero Shoes by you, through your affiliate link or the promotional assets we give you.Â </p><p>In addition to the commission youâ€™ll earn from your referralâ€™s first purchase, Xero Shoes offers â€œLifetime Commissions.â€ This means that youâ€™ll earn commissions on all the future purchases your referred customer makes, regardless of how or when they come back to XeroShoes.com or XeroShoes.eu.</p><p><strong>Still have questions? EmailÂ affiliates@xeroshoes.com.</strong></p>",
