        "faq_item_TbV7hD": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "I want to promote a particular product or point to a specific page. How do I do that?",
            "answer": "",
            "answer_html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are 2 ways to do that, one if you </span><b>donâ€™t have</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> your own website (or are promoting somewhere other than your site, like Facebook), and the other if you </span><b>do have</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> your own website.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are the instructions for each of those options:</span><b></b></p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\"><b>If you donâ€™t have a website or are promoting somewhere other than your site:</b></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Â </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To link to a specific page, either with a ready-made banner or a regular text link, go to your affiliate dashboard, then click on â€œPromotionsâ€ then â€œBanners and Links.â€ From there, you can search for a particular asset, like â€œPrioâ€ to find direct links to the Prio page or â€œShoe Finderâ€ to get a link to our </span><a href=\"/pages/shoe-finder\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shoe Finder Quiz</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2.jpeg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6244326\" src=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2-300x137.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"137\" srcset=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2-300x137.jpeg 300w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2-385x175.jpeg 385w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2-150x68.jpeg 150w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-2.jpeg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If the page you want to promote isnâ€™t listed here, you can create a â€œDynamic Linkâ€ to that page. Watch </span><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hQnO6YtWBfqh0atltZVNQbOgRJ19BZLs/view\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">this video</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to learn how.</span></p><ol><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>If you have your own website and want to promote a specific product/page:</b></li></ol><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have your own site, you can use â€œDirect Linkingâ€ to promote any page/product on our websiteâ€¦ and you donâ€™t need to use your affiliate link. Also, you can use either the banners/images we provide, or your own images.Â </span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To set up Direct Linking, go to your affiliate dashboard, then click on Promotions, then click on Direct Link URLs.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fill in your domainâ€™s name in the â€œPatternâ€ section using the syntax *sitename.com*.Â </span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to see if youâ€™ve entered the Pattern correctly, enter the URL for some page on your site in the Real URL section and then click Check.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6244339\" src=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-300x130.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"130\" srcset=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-300x130.png 300w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-385x167.png 385w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-150x65.png 150w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When the testing passes, then click Add URL.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6244343\" src=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1-300x217.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"217\" srcset=\"https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1-300x217.png 300w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1-385x279.png 385w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1-150x109.png 150w, https://xeroshoes.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-1.png 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We will then review your Direct Link to make sure itâ€™s valid. If it is, we will approve it for use.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once your Direct Link is approved, you can then link to any page on XeroShoes.com or XeroShoes.eu with a â€œnormalâ€ link (e.g. &lt;a href=â€https://xeroshoes.com/somepage/â€&gt;Click Here&lt;/a&gt;), and our software will recognize that you sent that visitor and will link them to your affiliate account (if they first came to our site through your referral).</span></p>"
          }
