            "answer": "<p>We pay commissions monthly based on the following formula:</p><p>When a referred customer makes a purchase, any commission is marked as â€œPending.â€ To allow a grace period for returns or other adjustments, we wait for 30 days before the commission status is changed to â€œApproved.â€ Commissions are then paid on the 5th of the following month, with a minimum payout of $20.</p><p>For example, if someone you refer to our site makes a purchase on January 20th, the commission is marked as â€œApprovedâ€ on February 20th, and paid on March 5th, assuming your total commissions due is over $20.Â </p><p>If you havenâ€™t reached the $20 threshold, the commissions will â€œroll overâ€ to subsequent months until you have, and then you will receive your commission payment.</p>",
